      • getTagsByTagTypeAndParentTagCode

        List<TagChild> getTagsByTagTypeAndParentTagCode(String tagTypeCode,
                                                String parentTagCode)
        Gets a list of tag child objects with children flags, whose parent tag code is the specified tag code.

        When tagCode is null, return tags of tagTypeCode whose have no parent (root tags).

        Parameters:
        tagTypeCode - the tag type code
        parentTagCode - the parent tag code, may be null
        Returns:
        list of tag child objects with children flags

      • getTagsByTagTypeEntityAndParentTagCode

                                                       String parentTagCode,
                                                       Boolean isParentTagNull)
        Gets a list of tag entities per specified parameters.
        Parameters:
        tagTypeEntity - the tag type entity
        parentTagCode - the parent tag code, may be null
        isParentTagNull - specifies if tags should have no parents (root tags). This flag is ignored when parent tag code is specified
        Returns:
        list of tag entities

      • getPercentageOfAllTags

        List<TagEntity> getPercentageOfAllTags(double percentage)
        Gets a percentage of all tag entities. The percentage is randomly selected from all the tags. The random selection is done by assigning a random number between 0 and 1 for each tag and if that number is below the percentage value passed in as an argument, also between 0 and 1, then the tag is selected.
        Parameters:
        percentage - the percentage of all tags to return. Value between 0 and 1 (inclusive).
        Returns:
        the percentage of all tag entities
